node.title: MØAA - Euphoric Recall
node.description: Euphoric Recall is MØAA’s debut lp. Jancy Rae began writing and recording demos in seattle, she then moved to Venice and finished recording in collaboration with Andrea Volpato.
node.release: Euphoric Recall was released on WWNBB (We Were Never Being Boring) Collective on April 2, 2021.
